{"type": "article", "id": 27934, "title": "大米包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-08T07:24:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153519raLENCuhdTAc8fB0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://megane-mai.jp/\">めがね米</a>是由日本福井県鯖江市的三家小型企业共同推出的大米品牌，翻译过来就是“戴眼镜的米”。由于参与大米生产过程的人恰好都戴着眼镜的关系，他们在白色的包装上印上了三种不同的戴着眼镜的脸。这个简单而有趣的创意不仅仅为包装增加了辨识度，也让顾客对食品安全更加放心。你可以通过<a href=\"https://meganemai.thebase.in/items/3284229\">链接</a>购买到这款大米。售价为 1500 日元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021535174NDqm1f0MktTHaOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153518UPENJwOWiC5MId6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153518c6B9nI3hWlCNSJ4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153519mhZYPeb85O0pTdWt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44280443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}